57402,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:09:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73e62d0d5e2656083587a01d0a29ed02d7cae1ca","tid":1657402,"uid":51499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"de5135603d34a9b25f836097ddd8714de499089b","tid":1657402,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:08:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"056fb8903ab11ac7e8f47de7dfdeb6cee25fd707","tid":1657402,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:36:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccff2753683a755011a6c4c5a664884e622ac294","tid":1657402,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去大半年，大家既生活都過得好壓抑，好似見到有希望但係又唔知前路候點。有人或者係依大半年同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手離婚，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸又或者有家歸不得，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=37199a3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\